{"tid":995234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笑匠Kevin Hart演出《大富翁》電影","createTime":"2019-01-25T09:41:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T02:02:42.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38e19cf32a4aa2170c0844391a85a79481c77020","tid":995234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/ArticleBase/big/28274/115988.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2FArticleBase%2Fbig%2F28274%2F115988.jpg&h=4e87d32c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你覺得電影用「Emoji」做題材好離奇，咁「大富翁」應該更加令你大開眼界。《大富翁》以經典桌上遊戲為主題，據報荷里活著名諧星Kevin Hart與電影公司洽談至最後階段，似乎好大機會成事。<br />\nKevin Hart會演出之餘仲會負責製作，而佢嘅拍檔Tim Story正洽談出任導演一職。電影項目早於2015年公布，但直至最近先開始正式籌備拍攝。大富翁為全球最受歡迎家庭遊戲品牌，全球114個國家超過10億人玩過，遊戲被翻譯成47種不同語言版本。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=28274&amp;catid=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkgolden.com%2Farticles%2Farticle.aspx%3Fid%3D28274%26catid%3D21&d=Ev%2FgGGd3hbiNhm%2BUCJXp8NibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=a5639b04\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkgolden.com/articles/article.aspx?id=28274&amp;catid=21</a>"},{"pid":"5eb4147b0f74de6be74339829b1ca322a1622054","tid":995234,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:48:43.000Z","msg":"香港咪係大富翁既真實生活"},{"pid":"66cae94db1a156226283bb007443e53696795196","tid":995234,"uid":88841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"+&times;自傳"},{"pid":"05b60b29d9820161503fe11734029898100722f5","tid":995234,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T13:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3689fac21a567625dd01f8f206cc8516c239d085","tid":995234,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T14:00:50.000Z","msg":"依件黑鬼真係好撚搞笑<br />\n個樣又搞笑<br /